casebody.data:
Wednesday, August 29, 2001

MOTION DOCKET

01-1515. State v. Byrd.

Hamilton App. No. C-010379.

On discretionary appeal, motion for stay of execution, and motion to expedite ruling on motion for stay of execution and to expedite disposition of case.

Discretionary appeal denied, motion for stay denied, and motion to expedite denied as moot.

Moyer, C.J., F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.
